00:11:09.635 --> 00:11:11.403
<i> and not lose your oars,
 you're in great shape.</i>

00:11:11.403 --> 00:11:14.339
<i> I went through it with my
 brother in these boats</i>

00:11:14.339 --> 00:11:16.509
<i> that some boatmen described
