It was one of the largest

00:17:06.091 --> 00:17:07.760
desert estuaries
in North America.

00:17:07.793 --> 00:17:09.194
This is the western
flank of it

00:17:09.194 --> 00:17:11.429
<i> over on the Baja side.</i>

00:17:11.429 --> 00:17:14.466
<i> 3000 square miles, jaguars,
 Cottonwood forests,</i>

00:17:14.466 --> 00:17:17.368
<i> it took me two days
 to find this image.</i>

00:17:17.368 --> 00:17:22.074
<i> That's what
 we've changed it to.</i>

