<i> it's in the center,
 that's the delta.</i>

00:17:51.837 --> 00:17:53.805
<i> That little frappuccino pit
 I was paddling,</i>

00:17:53.805 --> 00:17:56.875
<i> it is on the middle
 bottom-third of that circle.</i>

00:17:56.875 --> 00:17:58.876
<i> So, I think if these rivers
 often as arteries,</i>

00:17:58.876 --> 00:18:00.879
<i> they help connect communities,</i>

