<i> They keep salinity
 in our water table at bay.</i>

00:18:07.185 --> 00:18:08.620
<i> Potentially you know,</i>

00:18:08.620 --> 00:18:11.456
<i> they connect our human spirit
 on some level.</i>

00:18:11.456 --> 00:18:15.994
<i> So, I think the Colorado
 today is</i>

00:18:15.994 --> 00:18:18.396
<i> a very powerful metaphor
 on so many levels</i>

00:18:18.396 --> 00:18:19.864
<i> because it shows us</i>

00:18:19.864 --> 00:18:21.366
<i> what happens
